**STOP AND REMOVE CONTAINERS
docker ps -a  (to get container names/ids)
docker stop containerName1 containerName2
docker remove containerName1 containerName2

**REMOVE IMAGES
docker images
docker rmi someImageName someImageID

**BUILD IMAGE with a Dockerfile
docker build -t YourimageName .

**Create/Run a container
docker run -it --name CONT_NAME IMAGE_NAME

**Go inside a container
docker exec -it CONT_NAME bash (or sh)





